 PROBLEM DEFINITION
 -------------------
 Small pharmacies struggle to track medicine stock levels, know when to
 reorder, and analyze which products generate the most revenue. This system
 solves that by modeling Suppliers, Medicines, Stock, and Sales, then using
 PL/SQL to automate sales processing, stock control, and reporting.

 ENTITY RELATIONSHIP OVERVIEW
 -----------------------------
 SUPPLIERS (1) ---- (M) MEDICINES (1) ---- (1) STOCK
                          |
                          | (1)
                          |
                        (M) SALES
================================================================================
